## Limitations
The findings are based on a limited number of sources and may not capture the full spectrum of opinions on the subject. Additionally, some sources may have inherent biases based on their institutional affiliations or the perspectives of individual authors. Further research could include a broader range of sources and more recent data to provide a more comprehensive view.